definition: in fact/in reality/as a matter of fact/in practice
practical/corresponding to reality/geared to practical situations
Line of Actual Control (LAC), separating Indian-controlled territory from Chinese-controlled territory

sentences.english: None of this will actually be decided at Bali.
sentences.chinese: 所有这一切实际上都决定在巴里岛。

sentences.english: At (long) last we found out what had really happened.
sentences.chinese: 最后，我们终于弄清了实际发生的情况。

sentences.english: He was supposed to give us advice, but this ideas were airy-fairy ideas.
sentences.chinese: 他应该给我们提些劝告，但他的主意都是不切实际的。

sentences.english: But that is the effect of relative dollar depreciation.
sentences.chinese: 但是，这却是美元相对贬值的实际结果。

sentences.english: One key problem when analyzing actual acoustic signal in phase space is how to reduce the noise and lower the embedding dimension.
sentences.chinese: 实际水声信号在相空间中分析时的首要问题是降噪。

sentences.english: And so, this actually is the input we needed to justify our criterion.
sentences.chinese: 这实际上是证明准则所需要的。

sentences.english: So when I woke up early this morning at 8am it was actually only 7am.
sentences.chinese: 所以，当我早上8点醒来时，实际上才7点钟。

sentences.english: Mancini had effectively lost his midfield.
sentences.chinese: 曼奇尼实际上输掉了中场。

sentences.english: So he can't know, yet, that death doesn't really mean anything in comics.
sentences.chinese: 因而至今他也不知道死亡在漫画中没什么实际意义。

sentences.english: However, this is very difficult to apply in practice on actual projects.
sentences.chinese: 但是在实际的项目中，这是非常难于付诸实践的。

sentences.english: Her brother is the king, but she is the effective ruler.
sentences.chinese: 她的兄弟是国王，但她才是实际的主宰者。

sentences.english: The results showed that the cathode pastes obtained can be satisfied with the request of user.
sentences.chinese: 经用户对阴极糊的实际使用，效果良好。

sentences.english: You could actually use a closure to do the resource setup and cleanup instead.
sentences.chinese: 实际上可以使用闭包代替该方法来建立和清除资源。

sentences.english: This book is really Juliette's story, told in the third person.
sentences.chinese: 全书实际上是以第三人称叙述了朱丽叶的故事。

sentences.english: The overpressure wave is actually the more dangerous of the two.
sentences.chinese: 实际上，这两类伤害中超压冲击波尤甚。

sentences.english: Indeed, pain and itch have been difficult to separate.
sentences.chinese: 实际上，疼痛和瘙痒一直以来都很难分开。
